   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>CHAPTER FOUR THE SERVICE OF THE BODY OF CHRIST Scripture Reading: Rom 12:1, 5; 1 Pet 2:5, 9; Rom 15:16; Eph 4:11-12; Acts 2:36; 2 Cor 4:5a; Acts 13:2; 1:8; Matt 28:18-19; Acts 4:31b; 1 Cor 2:4; Acts 6:10; 11:18; Rom 12:4; 1 Cor 12:7, 11; John 21:15-17; 1 Cor 14:1, 3-5, 12, 24, 31; Eph 4:16; 1 Pet 2:2; Col 1:28-29 OUTLINE Being the service of the New Testament priesthood of the gospel 1 Pet 2:5, 9: Being centered on the preaching of the gospel to save sinners and offer them as sacrifices to God Rom 15:16.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>The goal being to build up the Body of Christ Eph 4:11-12.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Taking Christ as the Lord Acts 2:36; 2 Cor 4:5a; Acts 13:2: According to Christ's heart's desire.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>For Christ's purpose.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Taking the Holy Spirit as power and authority Acts 1:8; Matt 28:18-19: Preaching the Word of God by the power of the Spirit Acts 4:31b; 1 Cor 2:4; Acts 6:10.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>Dispensing life by the Spirit Acts 11:18.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Taking the Body as the means Rom 12:5: Every member participating in service Rom 12:4; 1 Cor 12:7, 11.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Being the corporate service of the Body in the coordination of the Body Rom 12:5: Preaching the gospel to save sinners Rom 15:16.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Feeding the Lord's lambs and shepherding the Lord's flock John 21:15-17.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Perfecting the saints to build up the Body of Christ Eph 4:11-12.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>Prophesying, speaking for the Lord, to build up the church 1 Cor 14:1, 3-5, 12, 24, 31.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>The Body building itself up through every joint of the supply and through every functioning member Eph 4:16.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>The three steps of offering by the priests of the gospel in the Body: Leading sinners to salvation and offering them as sacrifices to God 1 Pet 2:9b, 5b; Rom 15:16.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>Nourishing the believers so that they may grow up and present themselves as living sacrifices to God 1 Pet 2:2; Rom 12:1.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Laboring and struggling in all wisdom to present every one of the saints full grown in Christ Col 1:28-29.</S>
   </TEXT>
